# SocialLinks Component Rules

## Overview
Rules and patterns for the SocialLinks component (`src/components/molecules/SocialLinks.tsx`)

## Purpose
Social media links with icon-based circular button design

## Rules

### Core Requirements
- ✅ **Data Source:** Import `SOCIAL_LINKS` from `@/constants/footer`
- ✅ **Icon Design:** Circular buttons with border (`w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-[#8a0028]`)
- ✅ **Accessibility:** Always include `aria-label` for screen readers
- ✅ **Hover States:** Background color change on hover (`hover:bg-[#8a0028] hover:text-white`)
- ✅ **Layout:** Flexbox with gap (`flex items-center gap-4`)
- ✅ **Icon Display:** Use text-based icons (`s.icon`) with proper font weight
- ✅ **External Links:** Social links should point to external URLs

## Code Template
```typescript
import Link from "next/link";
import { SOCIAL_LINKS } from "@/constants/footer";

export function SocialLinks() {
  return (
    <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
      {SOCIAL_LINKS.map((s) => (
        <Link
          key={s.label}
          aria-label={s.label}
          href={s.href}
          className="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-[#8a0028] text-[#8a0028] flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#8a0028] hover:text-white"
        >
          <span className="text-sm font-semibold">{s.icon}</span>
        </Link>
      ))}
    </div>
  );
}

export default SocialLinks;
```

## Implementation Details

### Data Dependencies
- Import: `SOCIAL_LINKS` from `@/constants/footer`
- Structure: Array of `{ label: string, href: string, icon: string }` objects

### Styling Classes
- Container: `flex items-center gap-4`
- Button: `w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-[#8a0028] text-[#8a0028] flex items-center justify-center`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#8a0028] hover:text-white`
- Icon: `text-sm font-semibold`

### Accessibility
- `aria-label` attribute for screen readers
- Semantic Link elements
- Proper focus states

## Design Specifications

### Button Design
- Size: 32px × 32px (`w-8 h-8`)
- Shape: Perfect circle (`rounded-full`)
- Border: Brand color border (`border border-[#8a0028]`)
- Icon: Small, semi-bold text

### Color States
- Default: Brand color text, transparent background
- Hover: White text, brand color background
- Border: Always brand color

### Layout
- Horizontal flex layout
- 16px gap between buttons
- Center-aligned items

